  <scopecontent id="aspace_4ca625be62f9cfc0a4740d04fba20b78">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Records include correspondence, meeting minutes, scrapbooks, membership lists, notes pertaining to induction ceremonies, printed and mimeographed material, photographs, awards, and other items pertaining to Sigma Gamma Rho.</p>  </scopecontent>
